The Telegraph - Calcutta : Business

 Crest inks deal with Lions Gate

 OUR SPECIAL CORRESPONDENT

 Mumbai, Aug. 25: RichCrest Animation, the US subsidiary of Shyam Ramannas Crest Animation Studios, has signed an agreement with Lions Gate Entertainment, a leading distribution house in the US. 

 RichCrest and Lions Gate have announced a three-picture co-production and co-financing arrangement to produce three state-of-the-art animated feature films.

 This is a milestone for Crest and a pioneering feat for the Indian animation industry. This partnership reflects confidence in our ability to produce full-length feature films of world-class quality as well as our recognition of Lions Gate as a content leader in the family space and a superior distributor of quality theatrical releases, said Seemha Ramanna, managing director, Crest Animations. 




